{
  "info": {
    "name": "LibroHub API v1",
    "description": "API REST de LibroHub.\n\nBase URL: {{baseUrl}}/api/v1\n\nAutenticacion: Bearer token en header Authorization.\nEl token se obtiene en Auth > Login y se guarda automaticamente en {{token}}.\n\nRoles:\n- reader: usuario estandar\n- admin: acceso completo\n\nCodigos de error:\n- 400: validacion fallida\n- 401: token ausente o invalido\n- 403: se requiere rol admin\n- 404: recurso no encontrado\n- 409: conflicto (email/documento/ISBN duplicado)\n- 413: archivo demasiado grande\n- 422: tipo de archivo no permitido\n\nVariables:\n- baseUrl: URL base (default http://localhost:3000)\n- token: JWT, se setea al hacer Login",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Endpoints de autenticacion y gestion de contrasenas. No requieren token salvo change-password.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Registra un nuevo usuario con rol reader.\n\nBody (todos requeridos):\n- name: nombre completo\n- document: numero de documento (unico)\n- email: correo electronico (unico)\n- phone: telefono\n- password: minimo 8 caracteres\n\nRespuesta 201: {}\n\nErrores:\n- 409: email o documento ya registrado\n- 400: campos invalidos o faltantes",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "register"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Juan Perez\",\n  \"document\": \"12345678\",\n  \"email\": \"juan@example.com\",\n  \"phone\": \"3001234567\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Autentica con numero de documento y contrasena.\n\nBody:\n- username: numero de documento\n- password: contrasena\n\nRespuesta 200:\n{\n  \"token\": \"eyJ...\",\n  \"role\": \"reader|admin\",\n  \"userId\": \"uuid\"\n}\n\nErrores:\n- 401: credenciales invalidas\n\n> El script de test guarda el token en {{token}} automaticamente.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"12345678\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Solicita un codigo de recuperacion de 6 digitos enviado al email.\n\nBody:\n- email: correo registrado\n\nRespuesta 200:\n{ \"message\": \"If the email exists, a reset code has been sent\" }\n\nNota: siempre responde 200 aunque el email no exista (no revela si el usuario esta registrado).",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/forgot-password",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "forgot-password"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"juan@example.com\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Validate Code",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Verifica que el codigo de recuperacion sea valido antes de resetear la contrasena.\n\nBody:\n- email: correo del usuario\n- code: codigo de 6 digitos recibido por email\n\nRespuesta 200:\n{ \"message\": \"Code is valid\" }\n\nErrores:\n- 400: codigo invalido, expirado o ya utilizado",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/validate-code",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "validate-code"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"juan@example.com\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Restablece la contrasena usando el codigo de recuperacion. El codigo queda marcado como usado.\n\nBody:\n- email: correo del usuario\n- code: codigo de 6 digitos\n- newPassword: nueva contrasena (minimo 8 caracteres)\n\nRespuesta 200:\n{ \"message\": \"Password reset successfully\" }\n\nErrores:\n- 400: codigo invalido, expirado o ya utilizado\n- 404: usuario no encontrado",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/reset-password",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "reset-password"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"juan@example.com\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"newpassword123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Cambia la contrasena del usuario autenticado. Requiere JWT.\n\nBody:\n- currentPassword: contrasena actual\n- newPassword: nueva contrasena (minimo 8 caracteres)\n\nRespuesta 200:\n{ \"message\": \"Password changed successfully\" }\n\nErrores:\n- 401: token invalido o contrasena actual incorrecta\n- 404: usuario no encontrado",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/change-password",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "change-password"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"currentPassword\": \"password123\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"newpassword123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Books",
      "description": "Gestion del catalogo de libros, comentarios, favoritos, PDFs y portadas.\n\nPublico: GET /:id/cover\nRequiere auth (reader o admin): GET y POST de comentarios/favoritos\nRequiere auth + rol admin: POST, PUT, DELETE de libros y subida de archivos",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Cover (publico)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "description": "Descarga la imagen de portada. NO requiere token, disenado para usarse en componentes Image.\n\nRespuesta 200: binario de imagen con Content-Type image/jpeg o image/png y Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400\n\nErrores:\n- 404: libro no encontrado o sin portada cargada",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/:id/cover",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "books",
                ":id",
                "cover"
              ],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "ID del libro (UUID)"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Books by Category",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Retorna todos los libros con status active agrupados por categoria.\n\nRespuesta 200:\n[\n  {\n    \"category\": \"Ficcion\",\n    \"books\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"uuid\",\n        \"title\": \"string\",\n        \"author\": \"string\",\n        \"coverUrl\": \"/api/v1/books/uuid/cover\",\n        \"categories\": [\"Ficcion\"],\n        \"category\": \"Ficcion\",\n        \"year\": 1967,\n        \"status\": \"active\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n]\n\nNota: libros sin categoria aparecen bajo \"Sin categoria\".",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/by-category",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "books",
                "by-category"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get All Books",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Lista todos los libros con filtros opcionales.\n\nQuery params (opcionales):\n- category: filtra por categoria (case-insensitive)\n- year: filtra por anio de publicacion (entero)\n\nRespuesta 200: array de objetos Book\n[\n  {\n    \"id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"title\": \"string\",\n    \"author\": \"string\",\n    \"isbn\": \"string\",\n    \"coverUrl\": \"string\",\n    \"categories\": [\"string\"],\n    \"year\": 2023,\n    \"pages\": 300,\n    \"language\": \"Espanol\",\n    \"publisher\": \"string\",\n    \"synopsis\": \"string\",\n    \"status\": \"active|coming_soon\"\n  }\n]\n\nErrores:\n- 400: year no es un entero valido",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "books"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "category",
                  "value": "Ficcion",
                  "disabled": true,
                  "description": "Filtrar por categoria"
                },
                {
                  "key": "year",
                  "value": "2023",
                  "disabled": true,
                  "description": "Filtrar por anio (entero)"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Book by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Retorna el detalle completo de un libro incluyendo comentarios, favoritos y si tiene PDF.\n\nRespuesta 200:\n{\n  \"id\": \"uuid\",\n  \"title\": \"string\",\n  \"author\": \"string\",\n  \"coverUrl\": \"string\",\n  \"category\": \"string\",\n  \"categories\": [\"string\"],\n  \"year\": 1967,\n  \"pages\": 417,\n  \"language\": \"Espanol\",\n  \"isbn\": \"978-0-06-088328-7\",\n  \"publisher\": \"string\",\n  \"synopsis\": \"string\",\n  \"status\": \"active\",\n  \"rating\": 4.5,\n  \"isFavorite\": false,\n  \"hasPdf\": true,\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"uuid\",\n      \"userId\": \"uuid\",\n      \"authorName\": \"string\",\n      \"avatarUrl\": \"data:image/jpeg;base64,...\",\n      \"text\": \"string\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nErrores:\n- 404: libro no encontrado",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/:id",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "books",
                ":id"
              ],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "ID del libro (UUID)"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Book (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Crea un nuevo libro. Requiere rol admin.\n\nBody:\n- title (requerido): titulo del libro\n- author (requerido): autor\n- isbn (requerido): ISBN unico\n- coverUrl (opcional): URL externa de portada\n- pages (opcional): numero de paginas (entero positivo)\n- language (opcional): idioma\n- publisher (opcional): editorial\n- synopsis (opcional): sinopsis\n- year (opcional): anio de publicacion\n- status (opcional): active | coming_soon\n- categories (opcional): array de categorias\n\nRespuesta 201: objeto Book creado\n\nErrores:\n- 409: ISBN ya registrado\n- 403: usuario no es admin",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "books"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Cien anos de soledad\",\n  \"author\": \"Gabriel Garcia Marquez\",\n  \"isbn\": \"978-0-06-088328-7\",\n  \"pages\": 417,\n  \"language\": \"Espanol\",\n  \"publisher\": \"Editorial Sudamericana\",\n  \"synopsis\": \"Una saga familiar en el pueblo ficticio de Macondo.\",\n  \"year\": 1967,\n  \"status\": \"active\",\n  \"categories\": [\n    \"Ficcion\",\n    \"Literatura latinoamericana\"\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Book (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Actualiza los campos de un libro. Requiere rol admin. Todos los campos son opcionales.\n\nBody (todos opcionales): title, author, isbn, coverUrl, pages, language, publisher, synopsis, year, status, categories\n\nRespuesta 200: objeto Book actualizado\n\nErrores:\n- 404: libro no encontrado\n- 403: usuario no es admin",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/:id",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "books",
                ":id"
              ],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "ID del libro (UUID)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Cien anos de soledad (Ed. especial)\",\n  \"pages\": 450,\n  \"status\": \"active\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Book (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Elimina un libro permanentemente. Requiere rol admin.\n\nRespuesta 204: No Content\n\nErrores:\n- 404: libro no encontrado\n- 403: usuario no es admin",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/:id",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "books",
                ":id"
              ],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "ID del libro (UUID)"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Add Comment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Agrega un comentario al libro. El autor se toma del token JWT.\n\nBody:\n- text (requerido): texto del comentario\n\nRespuesta 201:\n{\n  \"id\": \"uuid\",\n  \"userId\": \"uuid\",\n  \"authorName\": \"Juan Perez\",\n  \"avatarUrl\": \"data:image/jpeg;base64,...\",\n  \"text\": \"Excelente libro.\",\n  \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\"\n}\n\nErrores:\n- 404: libro no encontrado",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/:bookId/comments",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
